OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud turns
OL,6,Fpatchy and moves further north
OL,7,Fovernight, but returns in the west
OL,8,Flater, becoming more widespread.
OL,9,FPatchy showers for some in the west.
OL,10,FCooler than recent night but feeling
OL,11,Fmuggy in places.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FPatchy cloud to start the
OL,14,Fday but lifting and breaking,
OL,15,Fespecially in the east, to give
OL,16,Fanother hot day, but not as hot as
OL,17,Frecent days. Cooler in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
