OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,6,Fbrings rain, clearing west to much
OL,7,Ffresher and cooler conditions. Monday
OL,8,Fand Tuesday are then mostly dry with
OL,9,Fsunny spells. Temperatures a little
OL,10,Fabove average.
